                                <p class="journal">In R. Brown & S. Davis (Eds.), <em>Handbook of Neuroimaging Techniques</em> (pp. 145-172). Academic Press.</p>
                                <p class="abstract">This chapter reviews recent advances in EEG technology and their applications in neurological research, with an emphasis on high-density arrays and portable devices.</p>
                                <div class="pub-links">
                                    <a href="#" class="btn small">PDF</a>
                                    <a href="#" class="btn small cite-btn" data-id="paper4">Cite</a>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                        </li>
                    </ul>
                </div>
            </div>
        </section>
    </main>
    
    <!-- Citation Modal -->
